              },
              "name": "Player Core",
              "page": 455,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "text": "Elementals are creatures directly tied to an element and native to the elemental planes. Elementals don\u2019t need to breathe.",
          "type": "trait"
        }
      ],
